text:
1. Men and trees used to be good friends.

2. Overhydration is anabolic, but not good.

3. I wonder if the accumulated pain of nine periods is less than that of childbirth.

4. Most of modernity's blessings are related to cold. Refrigerators, ice cream, showers, drinks, windfans.

5. Smoking in small doses supposedly increases vascularity.

6. ATPases are Maxwell's demon internalized into our cells.

7. A friend told me he dreamed "pure red", the scariest nightmare.

8. Serrano says "raging against the dying of the light" is the worst thing one can ever do
